<note n="0465003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465003">〔本〕－【宋】</note>
<note n="0465004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465004">〔食〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0465005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465005">我樂＝樂我【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0465006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465006">法＋（而）【宮】</note>
<note n="0465007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465007">言＝為【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0465008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465008">〔諦〕－【宋】</note>
<note n="0465009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465009">耶＝也【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0465010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465010">及＝大【宋】</note>
<note n="0465011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465011">非是＝是非【三】</note>
<note n="0465012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0465012">不名＝名不【三】</note>
<note n="0466001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466001">見知＝知見【三】</note>
<note n="0466002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466002">非＝不【宋】</note>
<note n="0466003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466003">葉＝華【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0466004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466004">相＝想【宋】</note>
<note n="0466005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466005">弗＋（舍利弗）【宋】</note>
<note n="0466006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466006">〔之〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0466007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466007">言＝見【宮】</note>
<note n="0466008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466008">知見覺已＝所知見覺【宋】</note>
<note n="0466009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466009">差＝瘥【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0466010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466010">心＋（者）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0466011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466011">自＝復【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0466012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466012">有＝所【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0466013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466013">（得）＋實【三】</note>
<note n="0467001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0467001">（所）＋不【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0467002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0467002">牙＝芽【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0467003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0467003">輕＝嗅【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0467004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0467004">莫＝無【三】</note>
<note n="0467005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0467005">調＝掉【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0467006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0467006">當＝多【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0468001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0468001">不分卷及品【三】</note>
</p>
